(42, 'Staples', 'Daawat Basmati Rice/Basmati Akki - Super, 5 kg Pouch', 845.00, 'images/FOOD/fooditems/kohinoorfluffyrice5kg.webp', 5, 100, 'Versatile, fine, long-grained and perfectly textured. ‚ Basmati rice fit for a King. Daawat Super is aged to perfection. || \r\nNutritional Facts:\r\nEnergy 350Kcal, Carbohydate 78g, Sugars 0g, Protein 8.8g, Total Fat 0.47g, Saturated fat 0.1g, Trans Fat 0g, Cholesterol 0 mg, Sodium 1.7 mg, Dietary Fibre 1.6g, Calcium 5.9mg, Iron 1.08mg', '2021-05-22 16:35:57', 'food'),
(43, 'Staples', 'India Gate Basmati Rice/Basmati Akki - Feast Rozzana, 5 kg Pouch', 450.00, 'images/FOOD/fooditems/indiagaterice1kg.webp', 5, 100, 'India Gate Basmati Rice Feast Rozzana is defined by its long grains and amazing aromatic flavour. Having this rice is truly having a feast rozzana (a daily feast); combine it with your veggies and serve a nice pulao. Without this Basmati Rice, your biryanis will seem dull and tasteless. This is the perfect ingredient for different rice recipes. || \r\nBasmati rice has complex carbohydrates which mean that it can be digested easily and can be considered as an instant energy source. Rice has little protein, but the protein is rich in eight amino acids; plus as this is a gluten-free grain, people who are gluten-intolerant can consume this rice without problem.', '2021-05-22 16:35:57', 'food'),
(44, 'Oils', 'Fortune Kachi Ghani Mustard Oil, 500 ml Bottle', 117.00, 'images/Food/fooditems/fortunekachighani500ml.webp', 5, 100, 'Fortune Kachi Ghani Mustard Oil, traditionally extracted from the first press of mustard seeds, comes with a high pungency level and strong aroma. Being pure, our cooking oil retains its natural properties and mustard oil benefits. Its strong aroma and pungency spice up your cooking. ||\r\n\r\nNutritional Facts:\r\nFat - 100g, Mono Unsaturated Faty Acids - 66g, Energy - 900 cals.', '2021-05-22 16:48:33', 'food'),
